title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Mar 3 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Mar 3 2022
description:
Podcaster, rapper, author, and guru Zuby joins Clay and Buck to discuss provocative topics, such as covid psychosis, transgender swimmer. Led by Hispanics, Texas GOP primary turnout trounced Dems. C&B to sample BBQ and Rodeo in Houston where they are looking forward to broadcasting again from affiliate KTRH and meeting up with their radio friends Michael Berry and Jesse Kelly. Psaki on Russian energy. Texas caller on what to expect at Houston rodeo. Clay confesses to sometimes cursing while coaching his kids.
